      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "Top race despite the small field and it all hinges on the newcomer to the NT in REWARDS AND MORE (2). Former Victorian having first start this area and looks very well placed with the lightly weight. Arrives third-up from a spell and is unbeaten from three tries in that state. Best figures more than measure up and expected to hit the ground running. MOUGENOT (6) has had two runs since a break, the latest a win over 1000m at this track. Has won four of five starts since joining the yard and with the nice weight can run well now out to open class. BOY BIG (3) is a veteran sprinter with great starts this course and distance and looks a leading prospect. Winning rider Paul Denton stays aboard. Expected to feature again. DELAGO LAD (4) is very well weighted for this and should be thereabouts. FLYING YISHU (1) cannot be underestimated despite carrying the big weight. Has superb starts for this and has won 3/6 fresh.",
